// Contexts directory — each business domain gets its own folder here.
// Phase 5 will add the first context: contexts/property/
// Follows the vertical-slice pattern:
//   contexts/<domain>/
//     domain/        — types, rules, constructors, events, errors
//     application/   — use cases, ports, DTOs
//     infrastructure/— repositories, adapters, mappers
//     server/        — TanStack Start server functions